{"parts":[{"text":"Give me the details of your tools and sub agents"}],"role":"user"}
{"parts":[{"text":"I have access to a variety of tools and can delegate to a specialized research agent.\n\nHere are the details:\n\n### **Tools:**\n\n*   **Date and Time:**\n    *   `get_current_datetime`: Retrieves the current date, time, and day of the week.\n\n*   **Expense Tracker:**\n    *   `add_expense_tool`: Adds a new expense record with details like date, amount, category, and notes.\n    *   `edit_expense_tool`: Modifies an existing expense record using its ID.\n    *   `delete_expense_tool`: Removes an expense record by its ID.\n    *   `search_expenses_tool`: Searches for expenses using various filters such as category, date range, or amount range.\n\n*   **To-Do List / Task Management:**\n    *   `add_task_tool`: Creates a new task with a title, description, due date, and priority.\n    *   `edit_task_tool`: Updates an existing task's details.\n    *   `delete_task_tool`: Deletes a task by its ID.\n    *   `complete_task_tool`: Marks a specific task as completed.\n    *   `search_tasks_tool`: Finds tasks based on filters like due date, priority, or status.\n\n*   **File System Management:**\n    *   `read_file_tool`: Reads content from a specified file.\n    *   `write_file_tool`: Writes content to a specified file (overwrites if file exists).\n    *   `edit_file_tool`: Replaces specific text within a file.\n    *   `append_file_tool`: Adds content to the end of a file.\n    *   `copy_file_tool`: Duplicates a file from a source to a destination.\n    *   `move_file_tool`: Relocates a file.\n    *   `delete_file_tool`: Deletes a specified file.\n    *   `clear_file_tool`: Empties the content of a file.\n    *   `create_directory_tool`: Creates a new folder.\n    *   `delete_directory_tool`: Removes a folder.\n    *   `rename_directory_tool`: Changes the name of a folder.\n    *   `list_files_tool`: Lists files within a directory.\n    *   `list_directories_tool`: Lists subdirectories within a directory.\n    *   `list_tree_tool`: Displays the directory tree structure.\n    *   `file_info_tool`: Provides information about a specific file.\n    *   `supported_formats_tool`: Lists supported file formats (details not available in the current context, but the tool exists).\n\n*   **Research & Web Browsing:**\n    *   `research_agent`: Performs deep research and retrieves live web data.\n    *   `web_reader` tools: Browse and extract information from websites when specific URLs are provided.\n\n### **Sub-Agents:**\n\n*   **research_pipeline**: This agent is designed for a full research workflow: planning, parallel searching, collecting information, and generating a comprehensive report.\n\nHow can I assist you with these capabilities today?","thought_signature":"CukGAb4-9vv2fHD6nDNvA0O_xuEt8ilvBIVhoSVJG6pv1WABM1OzRqYFOVdrp4gN0X0MDyUrhdVR3_yc5uZ2Ze489T5juYX6UN9hLJ_F822k5bxCX2Vk2GtKbr4O2mTE9Zo8pAOVYWYulLsApQ2XVclU4PeqLDpaa284tETvK7kgQFnRe4u0izyPjNdJrZNh8dRStVU9NA1XQZcQNloGWKxzz69ZyQnRgSNmvFZPes8mOJNuEq7GRi_aJyR7mAG2BNuXlA9kKFi-kEnro_qEKkY8RCiiS5b-9oq371lWxqGteMT2OJrERHmCLP2dNhdCN2E2-LkBVCJsLkoK_LKys7nQfpUZDtTCxBeFL3t0n1_dOoePMjr3xeBPpIAPcsRKWjvKr5SDHyDfoP8rozbwm4_MvMqMcxx6yooF-9z6AaePEFNF2imXDp9PrltTpM6Vr_Y0xVgiOEaEgmLDQ-1ieMcVh65nM3iYbyNgyvB6YsMjy_LXwzXQQuMmKHRAF0F4s8LR0Iwb3wwGDh5-9NZMV8Tp0pDkk0H6zWt57NDZ81gBBRuA9NEx7z02-hX9fmDzGDxgH1EbXpuIeg4RZCX1KDnu0CZQGkKVNjoUcJctv2aqEto8KhW7Q35-5_KJGxHI6kUpr4KSBb36ulPfS1v9zoG5UVIWNAeCk3xJqq_Qlfvi3kvm71ngCTH0OyiulQa6NH7xUJ8knWXlnoZHI_EEHMdiGVcnF-XDrjY0rH8ih3Ss7bRgAczBLiDgZs4-PLYVDbucHR5f3m24S1MId7u7Q-cKCyKtgOKVEWozgocbVh0GDqI6KYnlynXW1UOR1zYQJkXrgT_XIYxWoX2DArs6ZFwuaBlak_AXaiYHkWjA2OP4I3W2nqKMGVmCwP7jjKTR2xIswrIcPAo2j1GKO8In-Bfd-JZLazY6DwxgtfgKue3JfhQUYscCnj2IC1Sav0j1sy0TLekY-K2wK5f8wlzAwZdBow7VExC-IH-xg3H2FXIJ32hUhHLmtGniqqKac-TIKw7t9AUs8yXS3fpHqWNPrNyu9c_rTfz9c5qNPeTPPWA_0ykBWG7hSXLLrMM_DthYqU2alSNIxCyPLagj4Lx7j6nT5AnjiIyVqRkkySYCzulHweg2hICWtIK_kezWT-HCaRCbOMKB27V0a5YD"}],"role":"model"}
